  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                   1.525826504037705         41.5199           957.47          4006.06
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.710546790267057        -19.3350          -445.87         -1865.54
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.232992913510501         -6.3401          -146.21          -611.72
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.024306640886248          0.6614            15.25            63.82
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.022394354619918         -0.6094           -14.05           -58.80
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.584199086526477         15.8969           366.59          1533.81
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

